org.apache.flex.abc.semantics

Class ArbitraryOperandsInstruction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.abc.semantics.Instruction
      • org.apache.flex.abc.semantics.ArbitraryOperandsInstruction

  • public class ArbitraryOperandsInstruction
extends Instruction
    An ArbitraryOperandsInstruction holds an array of operands as specified by the caller, or in some special cases as set by a fixup pass.
